        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-60664a93-2795-4e38-9e48-a4433b594e6b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-60664a93-2795-4e38-9e48-a4433b594e6b">
                Mrs. Castle
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-60664a93-2795-4e38-9e48-a4433b594e6b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-24/debates/abd0e71e-c2df-4145-8dce-371be442db99/EqualPay#contribution-60664a93-2795-4e38-9e48-a4433b594e6b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Chancellor of the Exchequer whether, in view of his decision to make a start in implementing the Chorley Report by granting some increases in salary for the higher grades of the Civil Service before the end of the year, he will also now make a start in implementing the principle of equal pay in the Civil Service, to which he is also committed.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-60664a93-2795-4e38-9e48-a4433b594e6b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-24/debates/abd0e71e-c2df-4145-8dce-371be442db99/EqualPay#contribution-60664a93-2795-4e38-9e48-a4433b594e6b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-b3d56844-4347-4b42-a1c4-9770ef7b5d72">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-b3d56844-4347-4b42-a1c4-9770ef7b5d72">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-b3d56844-4347-4b42-a1c4-9770ef7b5d72">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b3d56844-4347-4b42-a1c4-9770ef7b5d72">
                Mr. Glenvil Hall
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b3d56844-4347-4b42-a1c4-9770ef7b5d72" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-24/debates/abd0e71e-c2df-4145-8dce-371be442db99/EqualPay#contribution-b3d56844-4347-4b42-a1c4-9770ef7b5d72">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">No, Sir. The current economic situation does not admit even the start of the gradual implementation of equal pay in the Civil Service.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b3d56844-4347-4b42-a1c4-9770ef7b5d72" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-24/debates/abd0e71e-c2df-4145-8dce-371be442db99/EqualPay#contribution-b3d56844-4347-4b42-a1c4-9770ef7b5d72">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-6e2f9466-b259-400a-a4a3-312dd18303bb">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-6e2f9466-b259-400a-a4a3-312dd18303bb">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-6e2f9466-b259-400a-a4a3-312dd18303bb">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6e2f9466-b259-400a-a4a3-312dd18303bb">
                Mrs. Castle
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6e2f9466-b259-400a-a4a3-312dd18303bb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-24/debates/abd0e71e-c2df-4145-8dce-371be442db99/EqualPay#contribution-6e2f9466-b259-400a-a4a3-312dd18303bb">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is it not equally important to make a gesture to the long-frustrated women of the Civil Service? In view of the fact that a start is being made in other directions despite the inflationary risk, will not my right hon. Friend make a start here, too, by at least equalising the incremental scales for men and women in the Civil Service?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6e2f9466-b259-400a-a4a3-312dd18303bb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-24/debates/abd0e71e-c2df-4145-8dce-371be442db99/EqualPay#contribution-6e2f9466-b259-400a-a4a3-312dd18303bb">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-311a55a5-f06a-4741-b5c1-f211aae7f4a3">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-311a55a5-f06a-4741-b5c1-f211aae7f4a3">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-311a55a5-f06a-4741-b5c1-f211aae7f4a3">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-311a55a5-f06a-4741-b5c1-f211aae7f4a3">
                Mr. Glenvil Hall
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-311a55a5-f06a-4741-b5c1-f211aae7f4a3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-24/debates/abd0e71e-c2df-4145-8dce-371be442db99/EqualPay#contribution-311a55a5-f06a-4741-b5c1-f211aae7f4a3">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The two are hardly on all fours. The cost of implementing the Report of the Chorley Commission will not be more than £400,000 spread over a number of years, but to start <span id="2025" class="column-number" data-column-number="2025"></span> implementing equal pay in the Civil Service would cost at least £10 million in the first year—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-311a55a5-f06a-4741-b5c1-f211aae7f4a3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-24/debates/abd0e71e-c2df-4145-8dce-371be442db99/EqualPay#contribution-311a55a5-f06a-4741-b5c1-f211aae7f4a3">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-7b3eeb1f-b1ef-456c-b686-f82857874b1d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-7b3eeb1f-b1ef-456c-b686-f82857874b1d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
